        "body_text": "Compare A. Bellanger: Les concepts de cause, et l\u2019activit\u00e9 intentionelle de l\u2019esprit. Paris, Alcan, 1905, p. 79 ff. In this, acquaintance with reality\u2019s diversities is as important as understanding their connection. The human passion of curiosity runs on all fours with the systematizing passion. \u21a9\ufe0e",
